GlitterEA
---------

GlitterEA is an example project to demonstrate how to develop and run JEE6 client applications with NetBeans and Glassfish V3. It belongs to a two part tutorial found under
http://log4ray.blogspot.com/2010/02/create-and-run-jee6-client-application.html

The application provides a very simple microblogging/chat service example with a Swing based client. The application contains a JEE6 EJB module along with a JEE6 client application module, combined within an enterprise application.

The checked in source contains the full NetBeans project.

The provided source code is licensed under the Apache V2.0 License, see
http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0

Enjoy!

